# Pantone Super Swatch

## Our biggest, single swatch sample yet

Sku#: PLV-SSWATCH

$ 18.00

Build Your Sheet

Our largest, single color sample format is perfect for graphic and packaging designers looking to hold bigger color swatches right in their hands. Pantone Super Swatches come in one large 8” x 7” color block. Select from any spot color in our Pantone Matching System (PMS). Larger swatches allow for better visualization and communication of intended colors with all stakeholders up and down your development and production chain.

